{"tid":1309201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612一早定性為暴動 集氣幫盧偉聰諗下今晚點兜啦！","createTime":"2019-07-12T06:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:57:17.000Z","uid":93837,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70cdc3593510785573e4890b45c36b86d029d0b7","tid":1309201,"uid":93837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"6月12日出既禁止集會通知<br />\n612定性為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xO2Sh32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxO2Sh32.png&h=60c2aa06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvwr6Xn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgvwr6Xn.png&h=44b81aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月15日盧偉聰記者會<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】警方把6月12日反修訂《逃犯條例》示威衝突定性為「暴動」，事隔5日，警務處長盧偉聰昨日會見傳媒時澄清，「暴動」說法是指當日有一小部分人行為涉干犯暴動罪，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒說整個事件是暴動」，大部分人示威者是和平示威；警</span></span>方至今拘捕32人，有5人與暴動罪相關。對於被指對示威者過分使用武力會否道歉，他未有回應。民陣批評盧偉聰並沒有撤回「暴動」定性，要求他問責辭職。<br />\n<br />\n今次你仲唔仆街.jpg"},{"pid":"5cb992f3b9b8631afa508591d2ae246c81370393","tid":1309201,"uid":93837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5eeddb0cbb1b318d900b1aad601d6e142cbf16e0","tid":1309201,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"7/7佢都仲未回覆<br />\n係咪要扔西瓜？"},{"pid":"6d1644ba28ff04072a3c881d44f57aa6e61ad8ad","tid":1309201,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c33677b3554d7ad52a2c1c9322f5c8bc8b5228","tid":1309201,"uid":93837,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"警務處處長蓋埋印架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個係警務處處長呀</span></